MATT: The lights swish. All right. So, to get you
guys up to speed as fast as I can-- this is a

00:10:59.910 --> 00:11:05.823
really long arc. The Briarwoods, being a family
that five years ago took over the city of

00:11:05.823 --> 00:11:11.983
Whitestone, where Percy hails from, murdered his
family, and he barely escaped with his life, years

00:11:11.983 --> 00:11:20.709
later, came back into the folds of Vox Machina's
existence, and it was decided to go ahead and hunt

00:11:20.709 --> 00:11:25.554
them down and save the city of Whitestone. Upon
arriving, they began to stir rebellion in the town

00:11:25.554 --> 00:11:32.087
against this horrible undead menace controlled by
Lady Briarwood herself. After this rebellion was

00:11:32.087 --> 00:11:37.558
incited, fires were burning, individuals were
killed that were responsible for keeping the

00:11:37.558 --> 00:11:42.316
people down and just generally bad people all
around were being slaughtered by our intrepid

00:11:42.316 --> 00:11:49.376
adventurers. They made their way into Whitestone
Castle, where they had uncovered some information

00:11:49.376 --> 00:11:53.458
about the ziggurat, a project in which the
Briarwoods had been developing something beneath

00:11:53.458 --> 00:11:58.015
the city of Whitestone, and discovered that
Percy's sister Cassandra, who was thought to be

00:11:58.015 --> 00:12:02.811
dead long ago, actually still survived and was
being kept in the castle. She joined the party as

00:12:02.811 --> 00:12:08.978
you guys fought your way down underneath the city
of Whitestone through a series of tunnels, finding

00:12:08.978 --> 00:12:16.112
yourselves unintentionally locked within a trap, a
retooled version of what was previously an acid

00:12:16.112 --> 00:12:20.106
distillery for the whitestone that's actually
mined from the surrounding mountains, and thought

00:12:20.106 --> 00:12:25.376
left for dead by the Briarwoods themselves. In
which Vax was charmed and taken along with them,

00:12:25.376 --> 00:12:26.998
and Cassandra showed herself--

